{"id":333,"date":"2019-02-28T08:22:47","date_gmt":"2019-02-28T08:22:47","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/vvs.jgg.mybluehost.me\/qbs.com.qa\/2019\/02\/28\/5-react-training-courses-for-beginners-5\/"},"modified":"2022-08-10T10:38:54","modified_gmt":"2022-08-10T10:38:54","slug":"problems-that-can-be-solved-with-ai-solutions","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/qbs.com.qa\/problems-that-can-be-solved-with-ai-solutions\/","title":{"rendered":"Problems That Can Be Solved with AI Solutions"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Every business tends to function in their own unique way. Even though their mode of operation may be completely different from one another, the problems that they face may be the common linking factor.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>This is where analytics and AI solutions come to the rescue. In recent years, artificial intelligence technology has positioned solutions to solve some of these long standing business problems. &nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\u2019s take a look 5 business areas where artificial intelligence solutions can make a difference.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>1. Fraud<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Online transactions are increasing by the second. While customers have the convenience of getting what goods and services that they need at the click of a few buttons, it also opens up the possibility of criminals hacking servers to gain access to confidential information and data.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Needless to say, there is a need to ensure that digital and mobile transactions are secure. Businesses retaining sensitive customer and financial data in the servers and cloud must make sure that it is adequately are protected from unauthorised access.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>This can be achieved with the help of AI powered solutions that can scan transactions and access credentials thereby preventing risk of potential fraud. As a results, online fraud, spamming, and other types of financial crimes have decreased dramatically.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>2. Customer Support<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Business success today largely depends on their standard and quality of customer experiences.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The expectations are high when transactions are happening round the clock. Therefore, the need to establish a strong and robust customer support capability is a necessity and not a luxury anymore.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Companies are making use of analytics and AI solutions that is enabling them to offer responsive customer support across all consumer touchpoints.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>This is enabling the business to offer data backed resolutions faster that in turn is helping to build their brand reputation and retain customer loyalty in the long run.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>3. Personalization<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Today, personalisation is what draws your customers to you.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>By being able to anticipate future customer needs by detecting behavioural consumer patterns in data and providing actionable insights based on its findings, business enterprises can take their customer experiences to a whole new level.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>This is possibly by utilising multiple customer connect channels to deliver an integrated yet custom designed user experience with the implementation of AI enabled solutions. Moreover, analytics also plays a role combined with looking at customer history and preferences to address their needs and expectations.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>With the help of AI, businesses now have the opportunity to create more personalised and collaborative experiences for their customers.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>4. Data analysis<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>With such massive quantum of data, business need requires some level of control. Businesses need to give due respect to analytics and digital ethics as part of their due diligence process.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Simply put, business enterprises must take the responsibility to make sure that the customer data that is collected via various touchpoints is secure from leakage or unauthorised access by hackers.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Business enterprises focus largely on leveraging <a href=\"https:\/\/qbs.com.qa\/analytics-ai\/\">analytics and AI solutions <\/a>in combination with Machine Learning technologies to derive useful and meaningful insights from the volumes of data at their disposal.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Final Thoughts<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Believe it or not, artificial intelligence has already made its presence felt in a big way amongst businesses. With the help of AI Solutions Companies, businesses are addressing their evolving needs or solving organisational problems in a streamlined and efficient manner.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Every business tends to function in their own unique way. Even though their mode of operation may be completely different <\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":7298,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"om_disable_all_campaigns":false,"inline_featured_image":false,"_monsterinsights_skip_tracking":false,"_monsterinsights_sitenote_active":false,"_monsterinsights_sitenote_note":"","_monsterinsights_sitenote_category":0,"_jetpack_memberships_contains_paid_content":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[1],"tags":[5,7,8],"class_list":["post-333","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-uncategorized","tag-business","tag-it-security","tag-it-services"],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v23.9 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>Problems That Can Be Solved with AI Solutions | QBS<\/title>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1\" \/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https:\/\/qbs.com.qa\/problems-that-can-be-solved-with-ai-solutions\/\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"en_US\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"article\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:title\